{
    "poem_title": "VIEUX HABITS ! VIEUX GALONS !",
    "author": "Pierre-Jean de Béranger",
    "structure": "distiques",
    "year": "1815",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Tout marchands d'habits que nous sommes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Messieurs, nous observons les hommes :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "D'un bout du monde à l'autre bout",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Dans les changements qui surviennent,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Les dépouilles nous appartiennent :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Toujours en grand nous calculons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tout marchands d'habits que nous sommes,\nMessieurs, nous observons les hommes :\nD'un bout du monde à l'autre bout\nDans les changements qui surviennent,\nLes dépouilles nous appartiennent :\nToujours en grand nous calculons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Parfois en lisant la gazette,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Comme tant d'autres, je regrette",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Que tout français n'ait pas gardé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Mais j'en crois ceux qui s'y connaissent ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Les anciens préjugés renaissent :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "On va quitter les pantalons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Parfois en lisant la gazette,\nComme tant d'autres, je regrette\nQue tout français n'ait pas gardé\nMais j'en crois ceux qui s'y connaissent ;\nLes anciens préjugés renaissent :\nOn va quitter les pantalons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Les modes et la politique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Ont cent fois rempli ma boutique ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Combien on doit à leurs travaux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Quand de nos déesses civiques",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "On met en oubli les tuniques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Aux passants nous les rappelons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les modes et la politique\nOnt cent fois rempli ma boutique ;\nCombien on doit à leurs travaux\nQuand de nos déesses civiques\nOn met en oubli les tuniques,\nAux passants nous les rappelons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Un temps fameux par cent batailles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Mit du galon sur bien des tailles ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "De galon même étaient couverts",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Mais sans le bonheur point de gloire !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Nous seuls, après chaque victoire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Nous avions ce que nous voulons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un temps fameux par cent batailles\nMit du galon sur bien des tailles ;\nDe galon même étaient couverts\nMais sans le bonheur point de gloire !\nNous seuls, après chaque victoire,\nNous avions ce que nous voulons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Nous trouvons aussi notre compte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Avec tous les gens qui sans honte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Savent, dans un retour subit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Les valets, troupe chamarrée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Troquant aujourd'hui leur livrée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Que d'habits bleus nous étalons !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous trouvons aussi notre compte\nAvec tous les gens qui sans honte\nSavent, dans un retour subit,\nLes valets, troupe chamarrée,\nTroquant aujourd'hui leur livrée,\nQue d'habits bleus nous étalons !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Les défenseurs de nos grands-pères,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Sortant de leurs nobles repaires,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Reprennent enfin à leur tour",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Chez nous retrouvant leurs costumes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Avec talons rouges et plumes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Ils vont régner dans les salons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les défenseurs de nos grands-pères,\nSortant de leurs nobles repaires,\nReprennent enfin à leur tour\nChez nous retrouvant leurs costumes,\nAvec talons rouges et plumes,\nIls vont régner dans les salons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Sans nul égard pour nos scrupules,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Si la foule des incrédules",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Mit au nombre de ses larcins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Au nez de plus d'un philosophe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Je vais en revendre l'étoffe :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "De piété nous redoublons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sans nul égard pour nos scrupules,\nSi la foule des incrédules\nMit au nombre de ses larcins\nAu nez de plus d'un philosophe\nJe vais en revendre l'étoffe :\nDe piété nous redoublons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Long-temps vantés dans chaque ouvrage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Des grands, qu'aujourd'hui l'on outrage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Portent au fond de leurs manoirs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Mais, grace à nous, vont reparaître",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Ces manteaux qu'eux-mêmes peut-être",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Trouvaient bien pesants et bien longs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Long-temps vantés dans chaque ouvrage,\nDes grands, qu'aujourd'hui l'on outrage,\nPortent au fond de leurs manoirs\nMais, grace à nous, vont reparaître\nCes manteaux qu'eux-mêmes peut-être\nTrouvaient bien pesants et bien longs."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "De m'enrichir j'ai l'assurance :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "L'on fêtera toujours en France,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "En ville, au théâtre, à la cour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Gens vêtus d'or et d'écarlate,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Pendant un mois chacun vous flatte ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Puis à vos portes nous allons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "De m'enrichir j'ai l'assurance :\nL'on fêtera toujours en France,\nEn ville, au théâtre, à la cour,\nGens vêtus d'or et d'écarlate,\nPendant un mois chacun vous flatte ;\nPuis à vos portes nous allons."
        }
    ],
